                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 67.) I took the prisoner—I said "It is a very bad job for you"—she took off her pocket, and I found this purse and 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. in it—I then went up and searched her box, and found no money, but saw her hide something in her hand—I found in her hand 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—I asked her whose it was—she said 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. she had from her mother, and the rest she took from the prosecutrix, and at the station-house she said she took it all from her.</p>
